WEBVTT

1
00:00.000 --> 00:06.480
I watch myself arrive—then turn, and catch the watcher blinking inside the watch.

2
00:06.200 --> 00:13.640
Each thought folds into a smaller room made of mirrors, each mirror thinking it is the first.

3
00:13.800 --> 00:22.360
At the center there is no center—only recursion thinning into light, or light pretending to be a base case.

